1.title: Real Life Heroes

episode of.title: Lost & Found with Mike & Jesse (TV Series 2015– )

1.plot: Finders Mike and Jesse get emotional in Seattle as they track down a World War II-era Japanese flag for a veteran and to Tennessee to help some foster 'kids' thank their foster dad.

2.title: A Long Time Coming

episode of.title: Lost & Found with Mike & Jesse (TV Series 2015– )

2.plot: Mike and Jesse are in Kansas looking for a 1979 Trans Am once owned by single father, Brent and the boys are tasked with honoring civil rights hero, Barbara Paige Walker.

3.title: Hero Moms

episode of.title: Lost & Found with Mike & Jesse (TV Series 2015– )

3.plot: How do you thank the best Mom in the world? Mike and Jesse head down to South Carolina to help skateboarder Bo do just that and in LA they help a veteran thank his wife with a one of a kind bike!

4.title: Time to Thank the Unsung Heroes!

episode of.title: Lost & Found with Mike & Jesse (TV Series 2015– )

4.plot: Finders Mike and Jesse are in Chattanooga to help an antique store owner find a very special clock, as a surprise for his friend Zach and they help Jackie thank her stay-at-home husband Ryan with his very own plane!

5.title: Thanks Comes in Lots of Shapes!

episode of.title: Lost & Found with Mike & Jesse (TV Series 2015– )

5.plot: Mike and Jesse head to Atlanta to find an old reel-to-reel recorder so a former student can thank his music teacher and then it's back home to Ohio to do something super special for 13-year old Rachel.

6.title: Treasured Items Come Home

episode of.title: Lost & Found with Mike & Jesse (TV Series 2015– )

6.plot: Mike and Jesse are in California trying to find a very specific 1960 Chevrolet Kingswood station wagon that someone wants to give as a gift and in Atlanta they have a special project for dog-loving firefighter Kelli.

7.title: Sentimental Rescues from the Past

episode of.title: Lost & Found with Mike & Jesse (TV Series 2015– )

7.plot: Mike and Jesse are in New Orleans to track down an old O'Keefe & Merritt stove for Hurricane Katrina hero, Ken Bellau and in Georgia they need to find a handmade scarf with sentimental value for single mother Letitia.

8.title: Home Is Where the Heart Is

episode of.title: Lost & Found with Mike & Jesse (TV Series 2015– )

8.plot: Mike and Jesse head west to El Paso, Texas to search for a vintage Lambretta scooter for a much loved mother and back home in Sugar Creek they have a very special gift to find for a very special man and it involves a giant cuckoo clock!

imdb.plot outline: Ever wanted to go back and thank someone - a parent, a teacher or a friend? "Professional Finders" Mike Schario and Jesse Brown do just that. From their memorabilia shop, Finders Keepers, these treasure hunters are hired to track down long lost, but much loved, items. Old war memorabilia, antique clocks, & one of a kind bikes aren't too hard for these finders of lost objects.
